'''''Riddles in the Dark''''' is a podcast hosted by [[Corey Olsen]], Dave Kale, and Trish Lambert that was released from 2012 to 2015 about the forthcoming [[The Hobbit (film series)|''The Hobbit'' film series]]. It is part of [[The Tolkien Professor]] podcast series and was produced by the [[Mythgard Institute]].

